---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="Miss Moley's 30th — Bordeaux | The Void"
	description="A birthday trip agenda for a weekend in Bordeaux — 30th July to 2nd August."
>
	<div class="b30-page">
		<!-- ============================================================
		     HERO / COVER
		     ============================================================ -->
		<section class="hero-cover" aria-label="Cover">
			<a href="/" class="back-link" aria-label="Back to home">&larr; back</a>

			<!-- Large "30" watermark behind content -->
			<span class="hero-watermark" aria-hidden="true">30</span>

			<!-- Wine glass motif -->
			<div class="hero-motif" aria-hidden="true">
				<svg viewBox="0 0 120 200" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="hero-motif-svg">
					<!-- Bowl — open at the rim, two separate strokes -->
					<path d="M 35 30 Q 30 70, 42 95 Q 50 108, 60 112"
						fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2" stroke-linecap="round" opacity="0.55" />
					<path d="M 85 30 Q 90 70, 78 95 Q 70 108, 60 112"
						fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2" stroke-linecap="round" opacity="0.55" />
					<!-- Rim -->
					<ellipse cx="60" cy="30" rx="25" ry="5"
						fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.8" opacity="0.35" />
					<!-- Wine surface -->
					<ellipse cx="60" cy="55" rx="19" ry="4"
						fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.8" opacity="0.3" />
					<!-- Wine fill -->
					<path class="wine-fill-path" d="M 41 55 Q 60 61, 79 55 Q 85 75, 60 106 Q 35 75, 41 55"
						fill="currentColor" opacity="0.18" />
					<!-- Stem -->
					<line x1="60" y1="112" x2="60" y2="165"
						stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2" stroke-linecap="round" opacity="0.55" />
					<!-- Base -->
					<path d="M 40 165 Q 60 170, 80 165"
						fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2" stroke-linecap="round" opacity="0.55" />
				</svg>
			</div>

			<div class="hero-content">
				<span class="hero-label">A Birthday Trip</span>
				<h1 class="hero-title">Miss Moley's 30th</h1>
				<div class="hero-divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>
				<p class="hero-subtitle">Agenda</p>
				<p class="hero-dates">30th July &mdash; 2nd August</p>
				<p class="hero-location">Bordeaux, France</p>
			</div>

			<!-- Scroll hint -->
			<div class="scroll-hint" aria-hidden="true">
				<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round">
					<path d="M7 10l5 5 5-5" />
				</svg>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- ============================================================
		     PERSONAL MESSAGE
		     ============================================================ -->
		<section class="content-section message-section">
			<div class="message-inner reveal-on-scroll">
				<p class="section-note">Not the views that we will see, I'm afraid</p>

				<p class="callout-text">
					FOR THE MOLE THAT <em>&ldquo;DOES NOT CARE&rdquo;</em> ABOUT HER BIRTHDAY
				</p>

				<div class="message-body">
					<p>
						As you turn 30 and obviously don't care about this &#128064; (will you read this, I wonder?) I thought it would be good to go somewhere you would not immediately guess. As you have found out, the trip is in Bordeaux and I'm glad you were over the moon when I told you about it &ldquo;?&rdquo;
					</p>
					<p>
						Maybe you even expected an agenda with the specifics but likely you don't expect anything at all...
					</p>
					<p class="message-standalone">
						Let's hope the early preparations were worth it.
					</p>
					<p>
						I'll take the chance to wish you a happy birthday early so that it is &ldquo;ticked&rdquo;, as you say. I love you lots and am grateful to be spending this time with you. I hope you enjoy the walks, food, views and fun mole times this weekend will deliver.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- ============================================================
		     QUOTE
		     ============================================================ -->
		<section class="content-section quote-section">
			<div class="section-inner reveal-on-scroll">
				<blockquote class="feature-quote">
					<p>&ldquo;Preparation leads to better outcomes&rdquo;</p>
					<cite>&mdash; Someone I agree with</cite>
				</blockquote>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- ============================================================
		     BORDEAUX INFO
		     ============================================================ -->
		<section class="content-section bordeaux-section">
			<div class="section-inner">
				<div class="section-header reveal-on-scroll">
					<span class="section-label">About the Destination</span>
					<h2 class="section-title-text">Bordeaux</h2>
				</div>

				<div class="ornamental-divider" aria-hidden="true">
					<span class="divider-line"></span>
					<span class="divider-fleuron">&#10043;</span>
					<span class="divider-line"></span>
				</div>

				<div class="bordeaux-intro reveal-on-scroll">
					<p class="bordeaux-tldr">
						<strong>TLDR:</strong> Bordeaux is an elegant, historic French city and UNESCO site, globally famous for its wine and stunning architecture.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="highlights-list reveal-on-scroll">
					<div class="highlight-item">
						<h3 class="highlight-title"><em>L'ambiance</em></h3>
						<p>Historic, sophisticated, and wine-centric.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="highlight-item">
						<h3 class="highlight-title"><em>Incontournables</em></h3>
						<p>The historic city centre, La Cit&eacute; du Vin museum, and the surrounding vineyards.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="highlight-item">
						<h3 class="highlight-title"><em>Les saveurs</em></h3>
						<p>Bordeaux wine, the local Canel&eacute;s pastry, and Entrec&ocirc;te &agrave; la Bordelaise.</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<p class="french-slang reveal-on-scroll">
					They also have some cool French slang I have not heard in a while &#127467;&#127479;
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- ============================================================
		     ORDER OF EVENTS HEADER
		     ============================================================ -->
		<section class="content-section events-header-section">
			<div class="section-inner reveal-on-scroll">
				<div class="ornamental-divider ornamental-divider-wide" aria-hidden="true">
					<span class="divider-line divider-line-wide"></span>
					<span class="divider-fleuron">&#10043;</span>
					<span class="divider-line divider-line-wide"></span>
				</div>
				<h2 class="events-title">Order of Events</h2>
				<p class="events-subtitle">Four days in Bordeaux &amp; beyond</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- ============================================================
		     DAY 1 — 30th July
		     ============================================================ -->
		<section class="day-card" id="day-1">
			<div class="day-card-inner reveal-on-scroll">
				<div class="day-header">
					<span class="day-number" aria-hidden="true">01</span>
					<div>
						<span class="day-label">Wednesday</span>
						<h2 class="day-date">30th July</h2>
						<span class="day-theme">Arriv&eacute;e</span>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="day-rule" aria-hidden="true"></div>

				<ul class="itinerary-list">
					<li class="itinerary-item">
						<span class="item-time">Afternoon</span>
						<div class="item-content">
							<h3 class="item-title">Land in Bordeaux Airport</h3>
							<p class="item-desc">Bienvenue en France.</p>
						</div>
					</li>
					<li class="itinerary-item">
						<span class="item-time">Check-in</span>
						<div class="item-content">
							<h3 class="item-title">Drop Luggage at Hotel</h3>
							<p class="item-desc">Freshen up and get ready to explore.</p>
						</div>
					</li>
					<li class="itinerary-item">
						<span class="item-time">Afternoon</span>
						<div class="item-content">
							<h3 class="item-title">Explore Old City Center</h3>
							<p class="item-desc">Wander the UNESCO World Heritage streets.</p>
						</div>
					</li>
					<li class="itinerary-item">
						<span class="item-time">Evening</span>
						<div class="item-content">
							<h3 class="item-title">Dinner Cruise?</h3>
							<p class="item-note">Under consideration</p>
						</div>
					</li>
					<li class="itinerary-item">
						<span class="item-time">Night</span>
						<div class="item-content">
							<h3 class="item-title">Moley Drinks &#127863;</h3>
						</div>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- ============================================================
		     DAY 2 — 31st July
		     ============================================================ -->
		<section class="day-card day-card-adventure" id="day-2">
			<div class="day-card-inner reveal-on-scroll">
				<div class="day-header">
					<span class="day-number" aria-hidden="true">02</span>
					<div>
						<span class="day-label">Thursday</span>
						<h2 class="day-date">31st July</h2>
						<span class="day-theme">Aventure</span>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="day-rule" aria-hidden="true"></div>

				<h3 class="day-destination">Day Trip to Arcachon</h3>

				<ul class="itinerary-list">
					<li class="itinerary-item">
						<span class="item-time">Morning</span>
						<div class="item-content">
							<h3 class="item-title">Dune du Pilat</h3>
							<p class="item-desc">Europe's tallest sand dune. The views are unreal.</p>
						</div>
					</li>
					<li class="itinerary-item">
						<span class="item-time">Midday</span>
						<div class="item-content">
							<h3 class="item-title">Pic Niq</h3>
							<p class="item-desc">Merryl fromagerie, charcuterie, cave &agrave; vin et &eacute;picerie fine de l'aiguillon.</p>
						</div>
					</li>
					<li class="itinerary-item">
						<span class="item-time">Afternoon</span>
						<div class="item-content">
							<h3 class="item-title">Paragliding &#9978;</h3>
							<p class="item-desc">
								Over the dune, if we dare.
								<a href="https://www.pyla-parapente.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="item-link">
									Pyla Parapente &nearr;
								</a>
							</p>
						</div>
					</li>
					<li class="itinerary-item">
						<span class="item-time">Evening</span>
						<div class="item-content">
							<h3 class="item-title">Dinner at La Fine Bouche</h3>
						</div>
					</li>
					<li class="itinerary-item">
						<span class="item-time item-time-alt">or</span>
						<div class="item-content">
							<h3 class="item-title">Dinner at La Tradizione Bordeaux</h3>
						</div>
					</li>
					<li class="itinerary-item">
						<span class="item-time">Night</span>
						<div class="item-content">
							<h3 class="item-title">Wines in Bordeaux &#127863;</h3>
							<p class="item-desc">When in Rome&hellip; or rather, Bordeaux.</p>
						</div>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- ============================================================
		     DAY 3 — 1st August
		     ============================================================ -->
		<section class="day-card" id="day-3">
			<div class="day-card-inner reveal-on-scroll">
				<div class="day-header">
					<span class="day-number" aria-hidden="true">03</span>
					<div>
						<span class="day-label">Friday</span>
						<h2 class="day-date">1st August</h2>
						<span class="day-theme">Terroir</span>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="day-rule" aria-hidden="true"></div>

				<h3 class="day-destination">Day Trip to St. Emilion</h3>

				<ul class="itinerary-list">
					<li class="itinerary-item">
						<span class="item-time">Morning</span>
						<div class="item-content">
							<h3 class="item-title">Explore Old Town</h3>
							<p class="item-desc">Medieval streets, limestone buildings, and endless charm.</p>
						</div>
					</li>
					<li class="itinerary-item">
						<span class="item-time">Midday</span>
						<div class="item-content">
							<h3 class="item-title">Winery Tour &#127863;</h3>
							<p class="item-desc">Taste the terroir.</p>
						</div>
					</li>
					<li class="itinerary-item">
						<span class="item-time">Afternoon</span>
						<div class="item-content">
							<h3 class="item-title">Lunch</h3>
							<p class="item-desc">A proper French lunch in the village.</p>
						</div>
					</li>
					<li class="itinerary-item">
						<span class="item-time">Evening</span>
						<div class="item-content">
							<h3 class="item-title">Dinner</h3>
							<p class="item-desc">To be decided &mdash; chef's surprise.</p>
						</div>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- ============================================================
		     DAY 4 — 2nd August
		     ============================================================ -->
		<section class="day-card day-card-farewell" id="day-4">
			<div class="day-card-inner reveal-on-scroll">
				<div class="day-header">
					<span class="day-number" aria-hidden="true">04</span>
					<div>
						<span class="day-label">Saturday</span>
						<h2 class="day-date">2nd August</h2>
						<span class="day-theme">Au revoir</span>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="day-rule" aria-hidden="true"></div>

				<ul class="itinerary-list">
					<li class="itinerary-item">
						<span class="item-time">Morning</span>
						<div class="item-content">
							<h3 class="item-title">Cruise Brunch</h3>
							<p class="item-desc">Brunch on the Garonne. A fitting farewell.</p>
						</div>
					</li>
					<li class="itinerary-item">
						<span class="item-time">Midday</span>
						<div class="item-content">
							<h3 class="item-title">Lunch at Les Dr&ocirc;les</h3>
							<p class="item-desc">One last proper meal before we go.</p>
						</div>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- ============================================================
		     CLOSING
		     ============================================================ -->
		<section class="closing-cover" aria-label="Closing">
			<div class="closing-content reveal-on-scroll">
				<div class="closing-motif" aria-hidden="true">
					<svg viewBox="0 0 120 200" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="closing-motif-svg">
						<path d="M 35 30 Q 30 70, 42 95 Q 50 108, 60 112"
							fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="round" opacity="0.25" />
						<path d="M 85 30 Q 90 70, 78 95 Q 70 108, 60 112"
							fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="round" opacity="0.25" />
						<ellipse cx="60" cy="30" rx="25" ry="5"
							fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.7" opacity="0.2" />
						<line x1="60" y1="112" x2="60" y2="165"
							stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="round" opacity="0.25" />
						<path d="M 40 165 Q 60 170, 80 165"
							fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="round" opacity="0.25" />
					</svg>
				</div>

				<p class="closing-message">Happy 30th, Moley.</p>
				<p class="closing-tagline">&Agrave; nous, Bordeaux.</p>
				<div class="closing-divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>
				<p class="closing-heart" aria-hidden="true">&hearts;</p>
			</div>
		</section>
	</div>
</Layout>

<style>
	/* =================================================================
	   CSS VARIABLES & FULL-BLEED WRAPPER
	   ================================================================= */
	.b30-page {
		--bdx-cream: #FAF6F0;
		--bdx-cream-deep: #F2EDE4;
		--bdx-wine: #722F37;
		--bdx-wine-deep: #5A1A22;
		--bdx-gold: #C5A55A;
		--bdx-gold-light: #D4BC7C;
		--bdx-ink: #2D2226;
		--bdx-ink-mid: rgba(45, 34, 38, 0.6);
		--bdx-ink-faint: rgba(45, 34, 38, 0.15);

		margin: -2rem -1.5rem;
		color: var(--bdx-ink);
		background: var(--bdx-cream);
		font-family: var(--font-serif);
		line-height: 1.7;
	}

	:global(.dark) .b30-page {
		--bdx-cream: #1A1618;
		--bdx-cream-deep: #141113;
		--bdx-wine: #C2727A;
		--bdx-wine-deep: #D4949A;
		--bdx-gold: #D4BC7C;
		--bdx-gold-light: #B89E5A;
		--bdx-ink: #E8E2D6;
		--bdx-ink-mid: rgba(232, 226, 214, 0.6);
		--bdx-ink-faint: rgba(232, 226, 214, 0.12);
	}

	@media (min-width: 768px) {
		.b30-page {
			margin-left: -3rem;
			margin-right: -3rem;
		}
	}

	@media (min-width: 1024px) {
		.b30-page {
			margin-left: -4rem;
			margin-right: -4rem;
		}
	}

	/* Selection */
	.b30-page ::selection {
		background-color: var(--bdx-wine);
		color: #fff;
	}

	:global(.dark) .b30-page ::selection {
		background-color: var(--bdx-gold);
		color: var(--bdx-cream-deep);
	}

	/* =================================================================
	   SCROLL REVEAL ANIMATION
	   ================================================================= */
	.reveal-on-scroll {
		opacity: 0;
		transform: translateY(24px);
		transition: opacity 0.7s ease, transform 0.7s ease;
	}

	.reveal-on-scroll.revealed {
		opacity: 1;
		transform: translateY(0);
	}

	/* Staggered itinerary items */
	.itinerary-item {
		opacity: 0;
		transform: translateX(-12px);
		transition: opacity 0.5s ease, transform 0.5s ease;
	}

	.revealed .itinerary-item {
		opacity: 1;
		transform: translateX(0);
	}

	.revealed .itinerary-item:nth-child(1) { transition-delay: 0.1s; }
	.revealed .itinerary-item:nth-child(2) { transition-delay: 0.2s; }
	.revealed .itinerary-item:nth-child(3) { transition-delay: 0.3s; }
	.revealed .itinerary-item:nth-child(4) { transition-delay: 0.4s; }
	.revealed .itinerary-item:nth-child(5) { transition-delay: 0.5s; }
	.revealed .itinerary-item:nth-child(6) { transition-delay: 0.6s; }

	/* Hero wine fill reveal */
	.wine-fill-path {
		clip-path: inset(100% 0 0 0);
		animation: wine-pour 2.5s 0.8s ease-out forwards;
	}

	@keyframes wine-pour {
		from { clip-path: inset(100% 0 0 0); }
		to { clip-path: inset(0% 0 0 0); }
	}

	/* "30" watermark breathing — like the Heart Sutra's enso-pulse */
	.hero-watermark {
		animation: watermark-breathe 10s 1.5s ease-in-out infinite;
	}

	@keyframes watermark-breathe {
		0%   { opacity: 0.04; transform: scale(1); }
		40%  { opacity: 0.025; transform: scale(0.97); }
		55%  { opacity: 0.025; transform: scale(0.97); }
		100% { opacity: 0.04; transform: scale(1); }
	}

	:global(.dark) .hero-watermark {
		animation-name: watermark-breathe-dark;
	}

	@keyframes watermark-breathe-dark {
		0%   { opacity: 0.06; transform: scale(1); }
		40%  { opacity: 0.035; transform: scale(0.97); }
		55%  { opacity: 0.035; transform: scale(0.97); }
		100% { opacity: 0.06; transform: scale(1); }
	}

	/* Wine glass gentle sway — starts after pour completes */
	.hero-motif-svg {
		animation: glass-sway 6s 3.5s ease-in-out infinite;
		transform-origin: 60px 168px; /* pivot at base */
	}

	@keyframes glass-sway {
		0%   { transform: rotate(0deg); }
		25%  { transform: rotate(1.5deg); }
		75%  { transform: rotate(-1.5deg); }
		100% { transform: rotate(0deg); }
	}

	/* Hero divider grows from center on load */
	.hero-divider {
		animation: divider-grow 1s 0.5s ease-out both;
	}

	@keyframes divider-grow {
		from { width: 0; }
		to { width: 3rem; }
	}

	/* Scroll hint — sits at bottom of hero, gentle bounce, fades on scroll */
	.scroll-hint {
		position: absolute;
		bottom: 2rem;
		left: 50%;
		transform: translateX(-50%);
		color: var(--bdx-ink-mid);
		opacity: 0.4;
		animation: hint-bounce 2.5s 2s ease-in-out infinite;
		transition: opacity 0.5s ease;
		z-index: 1;
	}

	.scroll-hint.hidden {
		opacity: 0;
	}

	@keyframes hint-bounce {
		0%, 100% { transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0); }
		50%      { transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(6px); }
	}

	/* Closing heart — gentle heartbeat pulse */
	.closing-heart {
		animation: heartbeat 2.5s 1s ease-in-out infinite;
	}

	@keyframes heartbeat {
		0%   { transform: scale(1); }
		14%  { transform: scale(1.15); }
		28%  { transform: scale(1); }
		42%  { transform: scale(1.1); }
		56%  { transform: scale(1); }
		100% { transform: scale(1); }
	}

	/* Day theme words — delayed whisper entrance */
	.day-theme {
		opacity: 0;
		transform: translateY(4px);
		transition: opacity 0.6s 0.4s ease, transform 0.6s 0.4s ease;
	}

	.revealed .day-theme {
		opacity: 1;
		transform: translateY(0);
	}

	/* Respect reduced motion */
	@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
		.reveal-on-scroll {
			opacity: 1;
			transform: none;
			transition: none;
		}

		.itinerary-item {
			opacity: 1;
			transform: none;
			transition: none;
		}

		.wine-fill-path {
			animation: none;
			clip-path: none;
		}

		.hero-watermark {
			animation: none;
		}

		.hero-motif-svg {
			animation: none;
		}

		.hero-divider {
			animation: none;
			width: 3rem;
		}

		.scroll-hint {
			animation: none;
			display: none;
		}

		.closing-heart {
			animation: none;
		}

		.day-theme {
			opacity: 1;
			transform: none;
			transition: none;
		}
	}

	/* =================================================================
	   HERO / COVER
	   ================================================================= */
	.hero-cover {
		position: relative;
